text: Table Rock State Park is a state park in the US state of Missouri. It consists of located in Taney County and Stone County on Table Rock Lake. The park offers a marina, two campgrounds, a mountain bike trail, scuba diving, picnic areas and shelters. == Related pages == * List of Missouri state parks * Table Rock Lake == References == Category:Buildings and structures in Missouri Category:State parks in the United States Category:Ozarks
title: Table Rock State Park (Missouri)
